#X text 57 66 You can also use [allpass.filt~] to implement a Phaser. It even has a feedback input for convenience. The thing is that [allpass.filt~] cascades 2nd order filters and has a Q parameter. You can explore it \, but note that in order to match the behaviour of stacking 1st order filters \, the Q parameter must be 0.5!, f 58;
#X obj 209 276 rescale~ 100 2000;
#X obj 150 350 allpass.filt~ 12 0 0.5, f 26;
